<title>UK: London gold fixes easier but off its lows.</title>
<headline>London gold fixes easier but off its lows.</headline>
<text>
<p>GOLD - Fixed at $340.15 vs $341.60 previously. Off overnight on</p>
<p>Belgian coin sales proposal but off low on short covering.</p>
<p>Fairly quiet support expected to hold.</p>
<p>SILVER - Unchanged at $4.72/$4.74 after early low. May try</p>
<p>$4.80 again where previous rallies capped.</p>
<p>PLATINUM - Off low at $418.00/$422.00 up $10.50.</p>
<p>PALLADIUM - Up $15.00 at $204.00/$209.00. Still tight.</p>
</text>
